  "componentDescriptions": {
    "CodeBlock": "Display de código con syntax highlighting. Theme: light / dark. Size: sm (12px) / md (13px). LineNumbers: yes/no. Wrap: yes/no (wrap long lines).\n\n🔑 ARIA:\n• <pre><code> native\n• Copy button aria-live anuncia 'Copiado'\n• Line numbers aria-hidden\n• Scrollable: role='region' + tabindex=0\n\n⌨️ Keyboard:\n• Tab al copy\n• Enter/Space copia\n• Arrow keys scroll en el block\n\n🎯 Focus:\n• Copy button destacado\n• Success state después de copy\n\nTokens: 14, prefijo cb-.\nWCAG 2.2 AA.\n\nFont: monospace (SF Mono, Menlo, Consolas). Syntax highlighting runtime (Prism, Shiki) — en Figma muestra estático.\n\nNO usar para: inline code (usa <code> con Typography). Para diffs usa componente especializado."
  },
  "variableBindings": {
    "cb/light/bg": "surface/pressed",
    "cb/light/fg": "text/primary",
    "cb/light/headerBg": "surface/hover",
    "cb/dark/bg": "surface/inverse",
    "cb/dark/fg": "text/onInverse",
    "cb/border": "border/default",
    "cb/radius": "radius/md",
    "cb/sm/fontSize": "type/xs",
    "cb/md/fontSize": "type/sm",
    "cb/sm/padding": "spacing/3",
    "cb/md/padding": "spacing/4",
    "cb/lineNumber/fg": "text/subtlest",
    "cb/font/family": "type/mono"
  },
  "_meta": { "lastUpdatedBy": "spec+enrich", "pipelineVersion": "1.0", "timestamp": "2026-04-17", "mode": "from-scratch-fast" },
  "_decisions": [
    { "what": "Theme light/dark (inverso al resto del sistema)", "why": "Code blocks frecuentemente se muestran en dark theme independiente del resto de la UI (developer preference, better contrast for syntax colors). Explicit Theme property.", "source": "common-patterns" },
    { "what": "Syntax highlighting es runtime, no modelado en Figma", "why": "Prism/Shiki aplica colors según token type. En Figma el código se muestra en color uniforme; el render final tiene highlighting.", "source": "common-patterns" },
    { "what": "Copy button first-class", "why": "UX crítico para code snippets. aria-live anuncia 'Copiado' para feedback accesible.", "source": "common-patterns" }
  ],
  "_foundationsRef": "foundations.json"
}
